Title : Acquisition of Land Act 1981
Text : '''Acquisition of Land Act 1981''' ([http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/1981/67/contents c 67]) is an [[Act of Parliament]] of the [[United Kingdom]], which concerns [[English land law]] and [[Compulsory purchase in England and Wales|compulsory purchase]].

==Contents==
The Act regulates the conditions for granting a "[[Compulsory Purchase Order]]".

